absolutely not tolerate this unfilial son.

22
00:02:13,240 --> 00:02:15,720
Father, don't worry about Miss Xu.

23
00:02:15,800 --> 00:02:16,930
I'll take care of it.

24
00:02:17,160 --> 00:02:20,320
