35
00:02:55,760 --> 00:02:59,680
I indeed chose the right person.

36
00:03:01,120 --> 00:03:02,040
Not at all.

37
00:03:06,240 --> 00:03:09,480
You want to investigate what happened to your parents at Fulu Restaurant.

38
00:03:09,480 --> 00:03:10,140
Because...

39
00:03:10,600 --> 00:03:12,320
It's been so many years

40
