70
00:04:45,040 --> 00:04:45,880
And this too.

71
00:05:03,720 --> 00:05:05,440
I've been here less than a year.

72
00:05:05,440 --> 00:05:07,000
You're asking about something from seven years ago.

73
00:05:07,000 --> 00:05:08,280
How would I know?

74
00:05:08,680 --> 00:05:09,480
No idea.

75
00:05:17,160 --> 00:05:18,040
Ma'am.

76
00:05:19,040 --> 00:05:21,320
How long have you been working here?

77
00:05:21,600 --> 00:05:23,440
At least twenty years.

78
00:05:24,000 --> 00:05:26,800
Even the manager hasn't been here as long as I have.

79
00:05:26,880 --> 00:05:28,880
Then I'd like to ask you something.

80
00:05:29,000 --> 00:05:30,680
Do you remember five years ago

81
00:05:30,720 --> 00:05:33,280
when the young master held his birthday banquet here?

82
00:05:33,280 --> 00:05:35,010
Isn't the young master insane?

83
00:05:35,040 --> 00:05:36,840
Why would he hold any banquet?

84
00:05:37,000 --> 00:05:38,440
I don't remember. I don't remember.

85
00:05:38,440 --> 00:05:41,500
If you two keep slacking off, I won't be so nice anymore!

86
00:05:52,280 --> 00:05:53,320
And these too.

87
00:06:27,600 --> 00:06:29,680
You've been leaving early and coming back late

88
00:06:29,680 --> 00:06:31,000
these days. What have you been up to?

89
00:06:31,000 --> 00:06:32,159
Oh please,

90
00:06:33,280 --> 00:06:34,610
mind your own business.

91
00:07:34,000 --> 00:07:35,880
The young master is here. Hurry up with those desserts,

92
00:07:35,880 --> 00:07:37,600
or we'll all be packing our bags and leaving.

93
00:07:37,600 --> 00:07:39,560
Yes, our restaurant used to be so quiet.

94
00:07:39,560 --> 00:07:42,040
Thanks to the young master, we now have all these distinguished guests.

95
00:07:42,040 --> 00:07:43,280
